Quickstrike:



Quickstrike screamed when he saw Megatron's face. He turned his tail 
and skittered off to a boulder lying near a wall. He hunkered down to 
the ground, tail low, chin inches from touching the ground. 

He poked the side of his head out from the side of the boulder, 
hearing a rowdy commotion. Dark Mouse was behind most of it. It 
looked like she was going psycho. He showed the left half of his 
long, scorpion body, trying to show that he was still there, and 
trying to get some of his pride back.
